Field Detail

labelId

protected String labelId
A custom label for the control.

disabled

protected boolean disabled
Specifies whether the control should be rendered as disabled. Default is active state.

onclick

protected String onclick
Specifies custom onclick event. Default is none. Note that this is used when the event information is missing. Otherwise, use 'eventPrecondition' attribute.

accesskey

protected String accesskey
Specifies custom acceskey (defined by HTML). Default is none.

tabindex

protected String tabindex
HTML tabindex for the form element. This value must be a number between 0 and 32767.

checked

protected boolean checked
Specifies the initial state of the form control. Default is unchecked.

onClickEventId

protected String onClickEventId
The name of the event handler (in the widget that contains the list) that will be invoked when the selection changes.

eventPrecondition

protected String eventPrecondition
The script that will be called before the submit.

updateRegions

protected String updateRegions
Update regions that must be updated.

globalUpdateRegions

protected String globalUpdateRegions
Global update regions that must be updated.

getOnclickScript

protected abstract String getOnclickScript()
Provides "onclick" event script for the control. If none specified then null should be returned. Note that the script is used also for Aranea events.

Returns:
The script or null.
